      <description>&lt;p&gt;I was invited to create visuals for 3 sets back-to-back for Insomnia Festival&amp;rsquo;s kick-off event at Storgata Camping (TromsÃ¸, Norway). The first two sets lasted about 1 hour each while the last one was 3 hours long.
