    <item>
      <title>Rickey Mouse saga</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/projects/live/rickey-mouse/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 19 Dec 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/projects/live/rickey-mouse/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;RMFH was a project led by Finnish artist, Pasi MÃ¤kelÃ¤. I initially joined this constellation in the role of support camera and video editor during their first performance which was &lt;a
  href=&#34;https://youtu.be/3J7kacIyDzE&#34;
    target=&#34;_blank&#34;
  &gt;live streamed from Punctum&lt;/a&gt; (Prague, CZ) in December 2020. From the following year, I began creating the live-visuals we used in the show. Conceptually and formally rooted in experiment, this project was really &lt;em&gt;fun&lt;/em&gt; to be a part of. I was able to come in and develop all the live-camera things I wanted to play with. I developed my practise of working with the simplicity of OBS Studio and pushing its limits by building visuals using chroma/luma keying, layering, collaging, multiple camera inputs and multiple projections.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
